txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Scarred ears from the beasts in the lands surrounding the Ranger-outpost at Tinnudir. You are to deliver the items to the Ranger Astiul at the outpost on the shores of Lake Evendim.
'I will see that these are given to those who can put them to good use.'
'If you gather ears from the beasts in the area and deliver them to me, I will see that they are put to use.'
Wardens of Ann√∫minas Task: Scarred Ears
Tinnudir, a Ranger-outpost on the eastern shore of Lake Evendim, is home to the Rangers of Evendim. There, at the outpost, a Ranger named Astiul awaits the return of scarred ears.
Deliver the scarred ears to Astiul at the Ranger-outpost of Tinnudir
You have been tasked with collecting scarred ears from the beasts surrounding Tinnudir. You are to deliver the items to the Ranger Astiul within the lakeside outpost.
Wanted: Scarred ears from the beasts in the lands surrounding the Ranger-outpost at Tinnudir.
